# Hero demo: npx aerin-agent → ask → diff preview → /undo.
# Regenerate: vhs demo/quickstart.tape (or let the demo workflow do it).
Output demo/demo.gif
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 620
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "npx aerin-agent"
Enter
Sleep 6s
Type "fix the failing test in this repo"
Enter
Sleep 25s
Type "/undo"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Type "/exit"
Enter
Sleep 1s
